{"id": 4413, "title": "Ticket #4413: Minor bugs in DRMAA exit signal functions", "description": "<blockquote>\nThere are a couple minor problems in our DRMAA library in the functions that query how the job exited. First, the minimum buffer size required by <code>drmaa_wtermsig()</code> should be much smaller. Second, <code>drmaa_wifexited()</code> should set its <code>exited</code> argument to zero if the job exited via a signal.\n\n<p>These changes will go into version 1.6.2 of the DRMAA external.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jul-17 10:41</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/18f511bbb74e05bad56be0e44390f490b4b587b1\">[40690]</a></span>: super minor edit to 8.2.2 version history item <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4413\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4413'); return false;\" title=\"Minor bugs in DRMAA exit signal functions\">#4413</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Jun-23 12:05</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/3d49466acf5136f76a3eb2cd1f3e600fb9bd74e6\">[40486]</a></span>: Docs for drmaa update to 1.6.2. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4413\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4413'); return false;\" title=\"Minor bugs in DRMAA exit signal functions\">#4413</a></span>  